features.description:
You know the {@spell Mending|XPHB} cantrip.
As a {@action Magic|XPHB} action while holding {@item Tinker's Tools|XPHB}, you can create one item in an unoccupied space within 5 feet of yourself, choosing the item from the following list:
- {@item Ball Bearings|XPHB}
- {@item Basket|XPHB}
- {@item Bedroll|XPHB}
- {@item Bell|XPHB}
- {@item Blanket|XPHB}
- {@item Block and Tackle|XPHB}
- {@item Glass Bottle|XPHB|Bottle, Glass}
- {@item Bucket|XPHB}
- {@item Caltrops|XPHB}
- {@item Candle|XPHB}
- {@item Crowbar|XPHB}
- {@item Flask|XPHB}
- {@item Grappling Hook|XPHB}
- {@item Hunting Trap|XPHB}
- {@item Jug|XPHB}
- {@item Lamp|XPHB}
- {@item Manacles|XPHB}
- {@item Net|XPHB}
- {@item Oil|XPHB}
- {@item Paper|XPHB}
- {@item Parchment|XPHB}
- {@item Pole|XPHB}
- {@item Pouch|XPHB}
- {@item Rope|XPHB}
- {@item Sack|XPHB}
- {@item Shovel|XPHB}
- {@item Iron Spikes|XPHB|Spikes, Iron}
- {@item String|XPHB}
- {@item Tinderbox|XPHB}
- {@item Torch|XPHB}
- {@item Vial|XPHB}
See the rules for the item in the {@book Player's Handbook|XPHB}. The item lasts until you finish a {@variantrule Long Rest|XPHB}, at which point it vanishes.
You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Intelligence modifier (minimum of once), and you regain all expended uses when you finish a {@variantrule Long Rest|XPHB}.

